id: pm-1pah
title: "CI: cache vitest/.cache + tsbuildinfo for incremental builds + faster tests"
description: "vitest writes a cache directory that speeds up subsequent runs; tsc supports incremental builds via tsconfig {composite/incremental:true} writing .tsbuildinfo. Cache both with actions/cache@v5 keyed on lockfile + source hash so warm CI is 30-50% faster. Today every CI run starts cold."
type: Issue
status: open
priority: 1
tags[4]: cache,ci,performance,pm-cli
