updated_at: "2026-05-16T22:07:50.563Z"
author: maintainer-agent
acceptance_criteria: "actions/cache restores .tsbuildinfo and vitest cache on warm runs; tsconfig has incremental:true; second consecutive CI run measurably faster than first; cache key invalidates on lockfile or source changes."
